Condition : 2 - Details and samples of all facing materials to buildings within the development hereby permitted shall be submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority before any above ground works are commenced on site. The samples and details shall include:

brickwork; 
cladding materials (where relevant);
window treatment (including sections and reveals); 
obscure glazing details (where relevant); and  
any other materials to be used.
	
The development shall be carried out strictly in accordance with the details so approved and maintained as such thereafter.
